5000|$|Renata Beger {{is one of}} {{the most}} known, as well as controversial, {{politicians}} in Poland, not only for her political activity, but also for her personality traits. She is often very frank <b>in</b> <b>her</b> <b>opinions.</b> <b>In</b> <b>her</b> first term <b>in</b> parliament, in an interview for the Super Express tabloid, she expanded on her sexual life with her husband, and declared she loved sex [...] "like horse liked oats". Her attempts at formal speeches were often failed due to gaffes such as calling United Nations Secretary-General Kofi Annan Annan Kofan on TV. Beger was frequently ridiculed by satrists and some artists, including singers and bands such as Paweł Kukiz or Big Cyc recording songs devoted to her.|$|R
